{
  "texts": [
    "Finally, interviews were conducted with developers of several tools to further ensure the inclusiveness of the tool selection.",
    "Concerning the inclusion and exclusion criteria, we identified two main potential threats to external validity.",
    "The first threat stems from the exclusion of tools that do not feature user interfaces.",
    "This criterion was set to focus on tools that are readily adoptable by the average researcher.",
    "However, earlier studies involving prototypes without interfaces still align with many of our findings."
  ]
}